						               													<description>Amanita is an enchanting set-collecting board game that will win over nature lovers and mushroom enthusiasts with its hand-drawn illustrations and unique mechanics. In the game, players take on the role of mushroom hunters, exploring the world of mushrooms in four different roles over four rounds. To win, they have to collect different species according to their goals for photography, research, trading (market) and cooking (dinner). Players who choose the right strategy can win various bonuses during the rounds, such as an amanita basket or gourmet dinner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In this medium-weight board game for 2-6 players, players place mushroom cards into their own basket and from their hand onto the field each round, creating four ever-expanding piles of mushrooms in the centre of the playing field. The game consists of four main rounds, with a round consisting of five turns. This makes the total playing time between 30 and 60 minutes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Mushroom picking is also aided by special rule modifier cards...&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher (translated)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
